1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:01,710
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:03,440
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,510 --> 00:00:05,210
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,980 --> 00:00:10,520
Stop weaseling your way out of it
and give me a straight answer.

5
00:00:10,980 --> 00:00:14,150
Say you'll leave Adele Group
and stay out of my marriage.

6
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:16,620
Put your money where your mouth is.

7
00:00:18,220 --> 00:00:19,360
If you can't,

8
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,490
then the deal is off.

9
00:00:22,990 --> 00:00:25,700
I'll even tell the chairman
what you're really after...

10
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,700
to get you kicked out of Adele.

11
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:36,440
(Episode 31)

12
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:48,890
Prove that I won't interfere
with her wedding?

13
00:00:50,590 --> 00:00:53,930
But at the same time,
I have to stop it.

14
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:07,870
To give Choi Yu Na
the proof she wants,

15
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:10,840
I'd have to be with someone
other than Park Min Jun.

16
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:18,720
But what if I married
into the Adele family...

17
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:21,690
so I'd be in a position
to stop her wedding?

18
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:27,860
What if this is the best way
to kill 2 birds with 1 stone?

19
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:38,770
We...

20
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:43,210
Why don't we get married?

21
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:05,030
The one who killed Dr. Baek
and staged it as an accident...

22
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,830
Did I spend the last seven years
with him without knowing?

23
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,400
You're Min Jun's father.
How could you?

24
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,640
No way.

25
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:20,910
It can't be you. Not when it comes
to Dr. Baek's accident.

26
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:29,420
If you're behind this,
like Jung Ran said,

27
00:02:29,990 --> 00:02:33,830
then how much do you really know
about the Temi Bio incident?

28
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:43,770
Choi Yu Na.

29
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:45,600
What happened with her?

30
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,440
As if reinstating her wasn't enough,
you approved our marriage?

31
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:52,240
What in the world are you thinking?

32
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:54,010
Sir.

33
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:58,350
Stay married for just one year.

34
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:02,420
Get back what's ours,
and you'll get your divorce.

35
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,840
Was this your plan all along?

36
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:22,610
From the moment you covered up
the false accusation,

37
00:03:22,670 --> 00:03:25,240
did you lie to Mother and me
with this in mind?

38
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:32,050
Why would I be afraid enough
to lie to you?

39
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:37,460
I've changed my mind since then,
and I have my reasons!

40
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:40,990
So stop arguing
and do as you're told.

41
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:42,360
My word...

42
00:03:43,090 --> 00:03:45,200
is law in the Adele family.

43
00:03:47,130 --> 00:03:49,930
What does Ms. Choi have on you?

44
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:56,270
After you changed your mind,
the only thing different now...

45
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:58,410
is that Ms. Choi is back.

46
00:03:59,210 --> 00:04:02,180
What did she do to get to you?

47
00:04:03,450 --> 00:04:07,420
How did she get you to reinstate her
and even approve this marriage?

48
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:10,620
Are you suggesting...

49
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:15,060
she's using something
she has on me...

50
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,960
- to control me?
- If that's not it,

51
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:21,170
then at least
please stop this wedding.

52
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,100
You two.

53
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:29,210
Have you given up your ambition
to take over Adele Group?

54
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:33,750
The fight for succession isn't over.

55
00:04:35,650 --> 00:04:38,480
If you want to succeed me
and take over Adele Group,

56
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,320
you will do as I say.

57
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:43,250
How dare you defy me
over something...

58
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:45,160
as trivial as a marriage
and call it blackmail?

59
00:04:47,090 --> 00:04:50,130
Marriage is nothing more
than a tool...

60
00:04:50,190 --> 00:04:51,700
to be used when necessary...

61
00:04:52,460 --> 00:04:54,200
to achieve your goals.

62
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,800
A tool?

63
00:04:59,940 --> 00:05:04,580
Am I your son,
or a pawn in Park Tae Ho's game?

64
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:07,750
If you consider me your son,
don't use my marriage as a tool.

65
00:05:07,810 --> 00:05:10,050
It's my marriage, and it's my life!

66
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:19,090
Being my son means...

67
00:05:21,260 --> 00:05:25,000
that your marriage and your life
are pieces on my board.

68
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,530
All for the glory of Adele.

69
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,700
You mean for your own greed.

70
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,810
Your endless, disgusting greed.

71
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,940
So what if it's disgusting?

72
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:42,750
My relentless ambition...

73
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,980
is what made Adele what it is today!

74
00:05:47,690 --> 00:05:48,920
Please, stop.

75
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:02,930
Just like Park Min Jun
is being forced into a marriage,

76
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:06,840
you'll also end up
in an arranged marriage eventually.

77
00:06:07,570 --> 00:06:09,910
If your marriage is going to be used
as a tool anyway,

78
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,080
then let me be the one to use you.

79
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,310
I never knew honesty...

80
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,850
could feel this painful.

81
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:23,250
You know how I feel about you,

82
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,690
and that's what you say?

83
00:06:28,330 --> 00:06:29,960
Do you even love me?

84
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,400
If I said I loved you,

85
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,530
would you even believe me?

86
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:39,770
Still,

87
00:06:42,410 --> 00:06:44,380
you could've at least lied to me.

88
00:06:47,010 --> 00:06:49,580
If you had, I would've believed you
without question...

89
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,190
and gladly played the fool.

90
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,600
I'm sorry,

91
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,640
but I don't want
to be used like this.

92
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,120
Help me.

93
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:28,820
I need this.

94
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:34,060
If you need me to love you,

95
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:36,560
I'll try.

96
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:40,830
You'll try?

97
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,770
Is this you trying?

98
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:02,050
Hugging me, clinging to me,
wanting to marry me...

99
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,290
all without love?

100
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:08,290
What on earth is making you
go to such lengths?

101
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:10,460
Who on earth are you?

102
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:13,200
Baek Jin Ju and Chloe are both dead.

103
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:17,100
Why do you have Baek Jin Ju's face
and go by Chloe's name?

104
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:21,540
You...

105
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,640
Just who are you?

106
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:27,180
Stop asking what I'm up to,

107
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:30,780
and start thinking
about what you want.

108
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,220
This marriage...

109
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:39,290
isn't a bad deal for you.

110
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,260
Am I wrong?

111
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:52,570
I'll be waiting for your answer.

112
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,180
Don't you ever...

113
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:08,350
mess with my head like this again.

114
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:12,390
Do I end this right now,

115
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:18,130
or just play the fool for you?

116
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,970
That's my decision to make.

117
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,290
I knew it.
You doesn't see me as his son,

118
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:49,190
just a pawn on his chessboard.

119
00:09:50,130 --> 00:09:51,230
Min Jun.

120
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,030
Is Adele still all you care about?

121
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,970
Adele, Adele, Adele!

122
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:07,450
You're no different from Father.
So stop trying...

123
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:10,050
to use my life.

124
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,220
And as for marrying Choi Yu Na,

125
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,350
that's never going to happen.

126
00:10:32,070 --> 00:10:33,070
You proposed?

127
00:10:36,570 --> 00:10:38,880
You proposed to him
and asked if you could use him?

128
00:10:39,810 --> 00:10:41,180
To use Choi Yu Na...

129
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:43,550
- and stop her wedding...
- I get that part.

130
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,690
Did Park Hyun Jun actually agree
to let you use him?

131
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,590
He said he'd think about it,

132
00:10:50,390 --> 00:10:51,620
but I think he was hurt.

133
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:53,960
He's more than hurt.
You broke his heart.

134
00:10:54,290 --> 00:10:55,990
His feelings for you were real.

135
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,500
What are those feelings...

136
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,530
good for, anyway?

137
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,170
To get revenge
on Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na,

138
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:07,410
I have to get married...

139
00:11:07,470 --> 00:11:08,470
Marriage?

140
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:11,240
- That's out of the question!
- James.

141
00:11:14,250 --> 00:11:16,150
When I laid Dr. Baek to rest,

142
00:11:16,410 --> 00:11:19,680
I promised him I'd give you
whatever you wanted. However,

143
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:21,650
marriage is where I draw the line.

144
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:24,760
You're talking about
ruining your own life.

145
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:26,790
No parent would allow that!

146
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:32,530
It'd break my heart
and Dr. Baek's too.

147
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,000
That's something I just can't do.

148
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:40,500
If you think of me
as a parent, as your family,

149
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:42,970
as your father,

150
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:45,040
find another way.

151
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:03,890
(Hanbit High School
62nd Graduation Ceremony)

152
00:12:08,430 --> 00:12:10,370
I'm sorry, James.

153
00:12:16,010 --> 00:12:17,010
Dad.

154
00:12:18,810 --> 00:12:20,340
My life was already...

155
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:24,280
completely ruined in that fire.

156
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:29,320
If it means I can finally take down
Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na,

157
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:34,190
I don't care
if I get ruined even more.

158
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:48,040
(Adele)

159
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:53,640
I'm sure you heard the news.

160
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,680
I heard you were reinstated.

161
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,650
Not my reinstatement,
but the wedding.

162
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:04,290
The chairman said
the wedding is back on.

163
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:08,130
You'll have a hard time
opposing it this time.

164
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:09,930
This time,

165
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,400
you make it sound
like something's different.

166
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:16,500
Let's just say the chairman and I...

167
00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:18,940
have gotten closer.

168
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:22,740
I took your advice and
gathered my courage...

169
00:13:22,810 --> 00:13:26,410
Did the Temi Bio card
finally work for you?

170
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:32,550
Don't try to deflect
with that nonsense.

171
00:13:33,250 --> 00:13:36,320
I'm just here to tell you
to take care of the wedding.

172
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:42,160
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

173
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:44,360
I know you're excited,

174
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,830
but I'm not like the chairman.

175
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,900
If my son doesn't want this,

176
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,140
I won't make him do it.

177
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:58,480
Are you saying you're going
to defy the chairman's orders?

178
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:01,280
I can't just ignore
what my son wants.

179
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:05,650
Just because you've gotten closer
to the chairman,

180
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:07,990
don't get too comfortable.

181
00:14:09,050 --> 00:14:12,620
When you're that close to someone,
even the slightest move...

182
00:14:13,060 --> 00:14:14,990
can get you hurt.

183
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:21,630
You should worry about yourself
before you start worrying about me.

184
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:25,070
Don't you think the person
who defies the chairman's orders...

185
00:14:25,770 --> 00:14:27,470
is the one who'll get hurt more?

186
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:47,890
So she's still going to oppose me,
even under the chairman's orders?

187
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:50,890
And what was that
about me getting hurt?

188
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:53,900
Is she saying she wants me
to get hurt or something?

189
00:14:55,370 --> 00:14:57,840
And why does she keep prying
about Temi Bio?

190
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,240
So annoying.

191
00:15:01,170 --> 00:15:03,340
I have leverage over the chairman,
so why...

192
00:15:05,610 --> 00:15:07,180
do I feel so anxious?

193
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,820
(Consultant, Chloe Lee)

194
00:15:25,060 --> 00:15:26,600
(Division 2 Director's Office)

195
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:33,170
He's not in his office.

196
00:15:36,710 --> 00:15:39,740
Director Park Hyun Jun
didn't come in today.

197
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:42,680
Really? I see.

198
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,150
And...

199
00:15:45,820 --> 00:15:47,520
I don't want you to get
the wrong idea.

200
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:49,690
Even though Choi Yu Na is back,

201
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:52,990
I'm not going to marry her.

202
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:56,230
Why are you telling me that?

203
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:59,430
Because I don't want Choi Yu Na
coming between us.

204
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,030
When my wedding to her
was being discussed,

205
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:06,270
you were the only one on my mind.

206
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:09,870
I was worried you'd misunderstand
and pull away.

207
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,840
Before I even knew
what was happening,

208
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:16,950
my heart already belonged to you.

209
00:16:21,890 --> 00:16:24,560
So you're over the woman who died?

210
00:16:26,690 --> 00:16:27,960
If it were Jin Ju,

211
00:16:29,190 --> 00:16:32,360
she would've wanted me to move on
and live my life.

212
00:16:32,430 --> 00:16:35,500
No. If I were her,

213
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:38,300
I would've told you to stay
in the past.

214
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:42,710
Not to move on so easily.

215
00:16:44,940 --> 00:16:46,240
Just stay right where you are.

216
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:52,120
Don't come to me...

217
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:54,450
when all I'll do is hurt you.

218
00:17:17,170 --> 00:17:18,740
I knew it.

219
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,910
You were flirting with my man,
acting all innocent,

220
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:24,720
so how are we supposed to team up?

221
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:29,290
If you're after Park Min Jun,
get lost.

222
00:17:29,290 --> 00:17:32,690
I don't need your help,
so get out of Adele right now.

223
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,460
What did I even do?

224
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:38,130
Are you really this upset
just because we talked at work?

225
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:41,470
Or are you that insecure?

226
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:48,310
Acting like this
won't get you anywhere.

227
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:51,540
Didn't you say
you're after the bio division?

228
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:53,880
If I were to tell the chairman...

229
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:57,610
But you haven't, have you?
And I know why.

230
00:17:57,950 --> 00:18:02,350
It's because you're actually
considering my offer.

231
00:18:03,390 --> 00:18:04,460
Then...

232
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:09,330
stop being impatient
and wait a little longer.

233
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:12,360
I'm working on a way to prove...

234
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:14,800
I have no intention
of ruining your wedding.

235
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,910
This is what you dropped yesterday.

236
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:27,480
You bought it from me,
so I couldn't just leave it.

237
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,480
Chloe...

238
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:34,990
Is she really dead?

239
00:18:35,290 --> 00:18:37,490
That's what I was told.

240
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:41,960
If you want, I can double-check
with my contacts in New York.

241
00:18:42,660 --> 00:18:43,660
That won't be necessary.

242
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,230
I'll look into it myself.

243
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:49,130
Okay. I'll be on my way, then.

244
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:00,340
(Temi Bio CEO Baek Jun Gi
and Daughter Dead)

245
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:01,450
(Vehicle Fire Complicates ID)

246
00:19:09,190 --> 00:19:10,190
At the time,

247
00:19:12,690 --> 00:19:15,460
the car was burned
beyond recognition,

248
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:21,060
so the bodies couldn't be
properly recovered or identified.

249
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:25,200
What if...

250
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:30,370
it's just like Min Jun said?

251
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,780
What if...

252
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:42,920
(Chloe)

253
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:14,220
I'll take this
as ordered by the chairman.

254
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:17,320
Whatever.

255
00:20:19,490 --> 00:20:22,190
He also told you to step away
from the gallery.

256
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:27,200
You might as well tell him
to kill me.

257
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,200
There's no way
I'm letting him take my gallery.

258
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:37,640
He's taking the gallery
from me, too?

259
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:42,310
Park Tae Ho, Kim Myung Hui...

260
00:20:43,780 --> 00:20:45,850
Do they think I'll just sit back
and take this?

261
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:54,660
(Eunhwa Trading)

262
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:56,490
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

263
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,230
Kim Myung Hui,

264
00:20:59,930 --> 00:21:02,270
you used Eunhwa Trading against me.

265
00:21:08,170 --> 00:21:10,410
(2019, Eunhwa Trading,
Seo Yi Bon, No. 5)

266
00:21:16,250 --> 00:21:17,980
What's on your mind?

267
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:21,120
I'm just a little scared.

268
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:25,120
Are you worried
that Chairman Park...

269
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:26,890
might be the one
who killed Dr. Baek?

270
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:28,690
For the past seven years,

271
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:31,700
it's terrifying
that I lived with him,

272
00:21:31,700 --> 00:21:32,700
knowing nothing.

273
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:36,600
More than anything,
when I think about Min Jun,

274
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:41,640
I don't know
what I'm supposed to do.

275
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:46,410
Right now, it's all circumstantial.
Nothing's confirmed.

276
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:48,450
Once you know for sure...

277
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:51,650
That's when you should worry.

278
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,880
The deal I confirmed
with Eunhwa Trading's CEO...

279
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:57,090
and the Temi Bio card...

280
00:21:57,920 --> 00:22:01,090
that got Ms. Choi reinstated
and her wedding approved.

281
00:22:03,390 --> 00:22:04,800
It's like the puzzle pieces
are coming together,

282
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:07,530
and the truth is already
crystal clear.

283
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:12,300
But I'm hesitating to put in
the final piece.

284
00:22:17,370 --> 00:22:19,940
I can't keep running from it, can I?

285
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,350
I have to face the truth, don't I?

286
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,060
With this,

287
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,500
I have to hit her
where it hurts most.

288
00:22:41,570 --> 00:22:42,570
(Eunhwa Trading)

289
00:22:42,570 --> 00:22:43,570
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

290
00:22:52,780 --> 00:22:55,010
Don't just stand there
looking defeated.

291
00:22:58,380 --> 00:23:01,520
Go confront Chairman Park.
Show him the torn page,

292
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:04,320
and prove your innocence.

293
00:23:07,290 --> 00:23:09,690
I'm sick of begging
that jerk Park Tae Ho.

294
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:11,860
I'm exhausted.

295
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,270
Even if I begged him over and over,
would he even believe me?

296
00:23:16,430 --> 00:23:19,000
He'd just say I tore it
to frame Kim Myung Hui,

297
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,510
and then bite my head off again.

298
00:23:23,610 --> 00:23:26,680
All he cares about is Kim Myung Hui.

299
00:23:28,950 --> 00:23:30,310
He even told me...

300
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:35,820
Keep a close eye on Myung Hui
and make sure she stays in line.

301
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:36,950
If by any chance...

302
00:23:37,890 --> 00:23:41,290
she suspects that I was behind
the Temi Bio incident,

303
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:48,800
make her believe you did it.

304
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,200
That's what you're here for.

305
00:23:56,170 --> 00:23:57,210
(Eunhwa Trading)

306
00:23:57,210 --> 00:23:58,410
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

307
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,810
That's what I'm useful for?

308
00:24:03,580 --> 00:24:05,420
I'm going to tear it all down.

309
00:24:07,850 --> 00:24:08,890
This time for sure...

310
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:12,220
I'll take down both Park Tae Ho
and Kim Myung Hui...

311
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:15,230
at once.

312
00:24:25,870 --> 00:24:27,800
That Oh Jung Ran...

313
00:24:28,100 --> 00:24:29,640
She's always doing useless things.

314
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:31,410
Should I get rid of it?

315
00:24:33,210 --> 00:24:34,280
Hold on to it for now.

316
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:36,410
You never know
when it might come in handy.

317
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:37,750
Yes, sir.

318
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:41,080
By the way, what should I do
about the gallery?

319
00:24:41,380 --> 00:24:43,520
It looks like Ms. Oh
will put up a fight.

320
00:24:46,290 --> 00:24:47,990
There's an exhibition coming up,

321
00:24:48,530 --> 00:24:50,090
and we have that deal
with Assemblyman Kwon.

322
00:24:50,530 --> 00:24:51,530
Yes, sir.

323
00:24:53,300 --> 00:24:55,070
Let's hold off on removing her
from the gallery.

324
00:24:55,700 --> 00:24:58,170
Having the director's position empty
ahead of important business...

325
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:00,000
wouldn't look good.

326
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,640
Understood.

327
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:06,440
The exhibit is just a smokescreen,

328
00:25:08,140 --> 00:25:09,880
but the deal has to go off
without a hitch.

329
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:12,320
Is everything on track?

330
00:25:12,550 --> 00:25:14,750
Yes, it'll all be ready soon.

331
00:25:16,650 --> 00:25:19,520
Good. And one more thing...

332
00:25:19,690 --> 00:25:21,390
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

333
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,060
Keep a close watch on Chloe as well.

334
00:25:24,090 --> 00:25:27,130
If she talks to the press
about Ms. Choi's reinstatement,

335
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:29,230
deal with it.

336
00:25:32,670 --> 00:25:36,810
I don't want any useless gossip
right before this major deal.

337
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,710
Adele's entire future is riding
on this deal.

338
00:25:41,610 --> 00:25:42,610
Absolutely no one,

339
00:25:43,810 --> 00:25:45,780
and I mean no one,
can get in the way.

340
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,650
Yes, I understand.

341
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,180
This was in your ledger, Ms. Oh,

342
00:26:18,850 --> 00:26:20,220
so I came to return it.

343
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:24,550
I was just about to send
for you anyway,

344
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:27,590
and here you are,
walking right in and admitting...

345
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:32,500
that you used Eunhwa Trading
to set me up.

346
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:36,700
Since I'm admitting it,
allow me to be blunt.

347
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:40,640
You're going to have to be
more careful from now on.

348
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:43,840
If I can't throw you in prison,

349
00:26:44,610 --> 00:26:46,710
I'm fully prepared to push you
into a trap instead.

350
00:26:48,110 --> 00:26:49,380
Seven years ago,

351
00:26:50,010 --> 00:26:52,550
- Temi Bio's CEO...
- Because I killed him?

352
00:26:54,620 --> 00:26:57,690
After looking into the Temi Bio case
and going as far as Eunhwa Trading,

353
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,590
were you that curious about
who killed him?

354
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:06,060
Were you trying to provoke me
to make me confess to the murder?

355
00:27:08,570 --> 00:27:09,570
But tell me,

356
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,270
you suspect Park Tae Ho too,
don't you?

357
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:17,540
I wonder who could have done it.

358
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:20,880
Me or Park Tae Ho?

359
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:23,680
Who would you rather it be?

360
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:41,100
How much longer do I have to wait?

361
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:42,600
Is this situation...

362
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:45,040
making you that uncomfortable?

363
00:27:48,710 --> 00:27:51,440
You said we were meeting
to talk about our wedding.

364
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:56,980
But you haven't said a word,
so I'm getting a little frustrated.

365
00:27:59,250 --> 00:28:01,250
I get it, but suck it up.

366
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,860
We haven't had dessert yet.

367
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:21,500
The cake here is amazing, you see.

368
00:28:23,910 --> 00:28:24,910
Have a bite.

369
00:28:34,050 --> 00:28:37,050
It has a nice, subtle sweetness,
doesn't it?

370
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:44,330
They used sweet potatoes
and chestnuts.

371
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:00,510
Excuse me.

372
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,610
Compliments of the house.

373
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,750
Thanks.

374
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:10,550
Don't you eat that.

375
00:29:11,990 --> 00:29:14,620
You remembered
I'm allergic to chestnuts?

376
00:29:18,930 --> 00:29:20,700
You care that I don't get sick,

377
00:29:20,700 --> 00:29:22,630
but won't even answer my question?

378
00:29:24,330 --> 00:29:25,500
A chestnut allergy?

379
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:36,050
It's loaded with chestnuts,

380
00:29:37,310 --> 00:29:38,680
so finish every last bite.

381
00:29:53,860 --> 00:29:55,170
Someone was murdered,

382
00:29:55,170 --> 00:29:56,830
and this is about finding out
who did it.

383
00:29:57,370 --> 00:30:00,100
Don't you dare play games
with the truth.

384
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:01,870
The truth?

385
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:05,580
Fine.

386
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:09,010
It's always "the truth"
with self-righteous types like you,

387
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:11,150
even when you can't handle it.

388
00:30:11,410 --> 00:30:14,220
If I couldn't handle it,
I wouldn't have come here.

389
00:30:15,690 --> 00:30:16,850
Tell me straight.

390
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:20,960
You, Oh Jung Ran,
murdered someone seven years ago!

391
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:28,030
You killed someone,
blinded by your own greed.

392
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:33,840
That's right.
I can even kill for my own gain.

393
00:30:35,670 --> 00:30:36,870
So today,

394
00:30:38,410 --> 00:30:40,510
I think I might just kill you,
Kim Myung Hui,

395
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:44,280
with that precious "truth"
you're so desperate for.

396
00:30:49,320 --> 00:30:51,990
Do you know why Eunhwa Trading's CEO
complied with me so readily?

397
00:30:53,690 --> 00:30:56,290
Do you think he was worried
about a measly bribery scandal?

398
00:30:58,760 --> 00:30:59,760
No.

399
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:03,700
It's because he couldn't let
their deal from seven years ago...

400
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:04,870
be revealed.

401
00:31:09,970 --> 00:31:13,410
What Eunhwa Trading procured
in exchange for that painting...

402
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:16,680
wasn't an object.

403
00:31:16,910 --> 00:31:18,350
(Additional painting for the CEO,
and also payment to Park Cheol Su)

404
00:31:18,450 --> 00:31:19,550
It was a person.

405
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,920
A person?

406
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,750
Someone secretive...

407
00:31:24,950 --> 00:31:27,320
who could build something dangerous.

408
00:31:29,430 --> 00:31:32,330
A device was needed
to blow up and incinerate a car.

409
00:31:35,330 --> 00:31:36,970
What Park Tae Ho wanted...

410
00:31:38,300 --> 00:31:39,340
was a bomb maker!

411
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:50,380
You...

412
00:31:51,950 --> 00:31:53,220
It's really you.

413
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,050
Baek Jin Ju.

414
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:06,630
Do you get it now?

415
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:09,600
No matter
how high and mighty you act,

416
00:32:10,530 --> 00:32:13,200
you've lived as a murderer's woman,
reeking of blood.

417
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,840
Just like me.

418
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:56,580
(Pearl in Red)

419
00:32:56,580 --> 00:32:58,610
What do you mean Park Hyun Jun
suspects who you really are?

420
00:32:58,610 --> 00:33:00,850
He asked to meet.
I thought it was about our wedding,

421
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:02,790
but he tested me
with a chestnut cake.

422
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:05,590
- Look into Chairman Park of Adele.
- Excuse me?

423
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:07,160
Being close to him,

424
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:09,090
I thought I knew him
better than anyone,

425
00:33:09,090 --> 00:33:10,830
but it turns out
I know nothing at all.

426
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:13,500
Fine. Do whatever you want.

427
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,870
Let's get married.

428
00:33:16,770 --> 00:33:18,770
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
